reviews.review_text: my first show perhaps the best show of 85'. i remember the space/drums and the rockin' 'satisfaction' oncore. a true sunshine daydream...

One Of The Last Best I was at this show. This was just about before the scene became stadiums. A small community college in SD. Easy in and out, mellow SoCal afternoon. 1st set was dull to me. But that 2nd set was an all timer! THE best Scarlet Fire EVER! She Belongs To Me Are ya kiddin'!

After this the scene seemed more cops and beggers. Ragamuffin lost kids looking for a free whatever....sigh....

Chula Vista Sep 1985 i had the great pleasure of attending this show. such good fun.  great venue.  as mentioned above, this was near the end of cozy shows.  this is a nice recording, thanks for making it available.
